===Etymology===
Borrowed from the {{bor|en|cmn-pinyin|-}} romanization of {{bor|en|cmn|匈奴|tr=Xiōngnú|sc=Hani}}. Possibly a {{doublet|en|Hun|nocap=y}}; their relationship to the Huns is disputed.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ʃɒŋˈnuː/|/ʃʊŋˈnuː/}}
===Noun===
{{en-plural noun}}
# {{lb|en|historical}} An ancient nomadic-based people that formed a state or confederation north of the agriculture-based empire of the Han dynasty.
